snippet.title: Yoshi's Crafted World - Launch trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Join Yoshi and explore a hand-made world, full of secrets to uncover in Yoshi’s Crafted World, out now on Nintendo Switch!

Official Website: https://www.nintendo.co.uk/Games/Nintendo-Switch/Yoshi-s-Crafted-World-1233953.html?c=purchase&utm_medium=social&utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=YoshisCraftedWorld%7Co3%7CLaunchTrailer%7Cw13
